# AmmoLang self-upgrade — refresh parser + build when sources change
@profile fastest
@verbose clean
@motto "AmmoLang self-upgrade · parse cache · module stamp"

seq ·
  say "AmmoLang self-upgrade — faster parse and build when sources change"
  self refresh
  fast path:aml path:gpy fastest
  say "AmmoLang modules warm — scripts should route through ammolang-run.sh"